WEBVTT

00:00:00.568 --> 00:00:02.064
NINETY SIX

00:00:02.678 --> 00:00:06.756
MISTER BAKER, az ir zent geven arestirt in Visoke Litovsk

00:00:07.521 --> 00:00:09.745
zent ir gevorn far- tsesheydt

00:00:09.745 --> 00:00:14.180
fun, fun di andere mentshn? ir zent geven mit di fraynt un mit, mit di froy?

00:00:13.697 --> 00:00:19.783
dos iz a ga- ikh veys nisht, dos iz a bisl a lengere geshikte vi azoy mir a- zenen gevorn arestirt, az

00:00:19.806 --> 00:00:24.038
ven mir zenen a- gevoyr gevorn az me UNK undz a gefar

00:00:24.038 --> 00:00:26.229
tsu vern arestirt, zenen mir avek

00:00:26.438 --> 00:00:29.199
tsu eynem a yid vos er hot gekent

00:00:29.526 --> 00:00:35.308
dortn eynem a vaysrus vos er hot aribergefirt iber di grenets. mir hobn im gegebn gelt

00:00:35.348 --> 00:00:36.742
mit zeygerlekh

00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:40.780
un z- u- un mir zenen geven, ikh, mayn froy

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:44.330
un tsvey kuzinen un a kuzinke, UNK bay akht mentshn

00:00:44.157 --> 00:00:46.058
vi hobn zey geheysn, di kuzinen?

00:00:45.658 --> 00:00:48.318
zey hobn geheysn RAYTER

00:00:48.848 --> 00:00:54.512
ye, Arn RAYTER, Hersh RAYTER. dos iz m- mayne FIRST kuzinen

00:00:54.720 --> 00:00:57.853
un zenen geven mit undz Khil SHPAYZMAN

00:00:58.483 --> 00:01:01.880
der vos er lebt in i- in Yis- Yisroel

00:01:00.222 --> 00:01:01.262
in Yisroel

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:04.569
un s'iz geven Yankl FREYDNRAYKH

00:01:04.709 --> 00:01:06.729
oykhet a khaver undzers

00:01:07.866 --> 00:01:14.019
UNK un nokh epes emetser denk ikh iz gevezn, yo, eyner a stolyar, Berish hot er geheysn

00:01:14.346 --> 00:01:16.213
hobn mir avekgegebn a sakh gelt

00:01:16.388 --> 00:01:20.168
mit zeygerlekh un m'hot genumen a, a vaysrus mit a ts-

00:01:20.168 --> 00:01:23.308
aza SANke, ir veyst vos a SANk- dos heyst a shlitn

00:01:23.863 --> 00:01:26.742
un m- s'iz geven di shney unterv- in yanuar

00:01:26.985 --> 00:01:29.226
un m'hot undz gefirt tsu tsum Bug

00:01:29.226 --> 00:01:30.978
vu s'iz geven di grenets.

00:01:30.782 --> 00:01:31.991
vos iz a taykh.

00:01:31.845 --> 00:01:33.357
der taykh, yo, Bug.

00:01:33.381 --> 00:01:38.623
un me z- hot, zey hobn undz aroysgelozt in vald, un dortn hot gedorfn vartn oyf undz

00:01:38.697 --> 00:01:43.449
eyner a, a, a mentsh, un er hot undz gezolt ariberfirn ⟨in⟩ di tsveyte zayt.

00:01:43.759 --> 00:01:45.778
ven m'iz aropgekumen in vald

00:01:46.088 --> 00:01:49.654
⟨hot men, iz⟩ ongekumen a, a, eyner a, a rus

00:01:49.654 --> 00:01:50.806
a sheygets

00:01:50.830 --> 00:01:56.274
un me hot undz ibergenumen, di tsvey mit di s- SANkes zenen avekgeforn tsurik aheym

00:01:56.415 --> 00:01:59.514
un er hot undz gefirt in azolkhe shneyen in vald

00:01:59.689 --> 00:02:00.766
un

00:02:00.766 --> 00:02:03.415
hot er, di, mayn froy's kuzine hot

00:02:03.415 --> 00:02:06.700
getrogn a PLECAK, geven shver, zogt er "gib mir, vel ikh im trogn"

00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:07.930
hot zi ⟨an⟩ im gegebn.

00:02:07.930 --> 00:02:12.494
me geyt a shtikl vegs, UNK bay, bay di nakht, in mitn di nakht. me dreyt zikh oys.

00:02:12.494 --> 00:02:13.655
er iz nishto.

00:02:14.083 --> 00:02:19.814
farshvundn, un mir blaybn in vald, un me veyst nisht vu m'iz, tsi m'iz oyf yene zayt ⟨OR⟩ m'iz oyf di zayt.

00:02:21.053 --> 00:02:23.273
vos tut men do? m'vet gefroyrn vern.

00:02:23.273 --> 00:02:26.043
s'iz vinter, yanuar, di frest dortn, shney

00:02:26.419 --> 00:02:32.707
zenen mir geganen a shtikl vegs, hot men gezen geshtanen a hayzke, dos heyst a ZIEMLANKA vos di arbeters arbetn in vald

00:02:32.832 --> 00:02:36.369
⟨hobn mir⟩ aza hayzke dortn. s'iz geven farklapt mit breter

00:02:36.763 --> 00:02:41.904
hobn mir dos oyfgerisn. m'iz arayngegangen in di ZIEMLANKA, un m'hot, biz s'vet vern tog.

00:02:42.197 --> 00:02:46.713
ven s'iz gevorn tog, bin ikh mit dem kuzin maynem, der Arn RAYTER

00:02:46.770 --> 00:02:49.540
⟨zenen mir⟩ aroysgan zen vu mir gefinen zikh

00:02:49.540 --> 00:02:51.960
m'iz opgan a shtikl vegs, zet men s'fort

00:02:51.981 --> 00:02:53.514
a shlitn aza

00:02:53.588 --> 00:02:57.750
un tsvey m- tsvey di folks politsey mit royte

00:02:57.773 --> 00:02:59.589
bender mit biksn

00:02:59.832 --> 00:03:04.399
un m'iz tsugekumen, hot men derkent dos iz geven der vos hot tsugenumen dem PLECAK

00:03:04.573 --> 00:03:08.499
hot mayn kuzin bald gezogt "du host undz tsugenumen a PLECAK. du host undz gefirt."

00:03:08.590 --> 00:03:12.740
dos iz geven azolkhe bandes. zey hobn gemeynt az mir zenen shoyn gefroyrn gevorn

00:03:12.740 --> 00:03:14.880
zenen zey gekumen tsunemen shoyn di

00:03:14.898 --> 00:03:16.008
di zakhn.

00:03:16.048 --> 00:03:17.527
dervayl hot men gelebt

00:03:17.652 --> 00:03:22.610
un m- zenen geven mit biksn. zey hobn undz arestirt, un m'hot undz avekgefirt in a

00:03:22.610 --> 00:03:25.036
a punkt, s'hot geheysn NIE- NIEMIROW.

00:03:25.887 --> 00:03:28.075
dortn hot men undz ibergenekhtikt

00:03:28.367 --> 00:03:32.799
un tsu morgns hot men genumen, gekumen ts- tsvey fun di N.K.V.D.

00:03:32.907 --> 00:03:34.335
mit ferd

00:03:34.543 --> 00:03:38.412
un zey zenen geforn. undz hot men getribn tsvelef kilometer

00:03:38.412 --> 00:03:39.380
tsu fus b-

00:03:39.943 --> 00:03:41.844
geyogt biz Brisk.

00:03:41.968 --> 00:03:43.632
⟨un⟩ in BREST LITOVSK

00:03:43.825 --> 00:03:46.142
hot men yetst undz arestirt un

00:03:46.142 --> 00:03:47.953
azoy iz geven biz m'iz a-

00:03:47.385 --> 00:03:49.218
ir zayt ale arestirt?

00:03:48.668 --> 00:03:50.214
ale arestirt.

00:03:49.613 --> 00:03:51.609
az ir zaynt geven tsuzamen mit der f-

00:03:51.609 --> 00:03:53.808
ah froy in, in tfise?

00:03:52.887 --> 00:03:56.745
ale, NO, UNK froyen zitsn nisht mit keyn mener

00:03:56.768 --> 00:04:00.204
froyen gezitsn UNK in an andere turme, un ikh in an andere.

00:04:00.801 --> 00:04:03.967
az ir hot nisht gevu- ir hot nisht gekent mit ir redn?

00:04:02.421 --> 00:04:06.785
NO, un ikh hob nisht gevust nakher fun mayn froy biz ikh bin aheymgekumen keyn Poyln.

00:04:07.129 --> 00:04:08.355
ven iz dos geven?

00:04:08.344 --> 00:04:10.717
bizn, bizn zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:04:10.622 --> 00:04:14.871
az oyf finef yor zent ir nisht geven in farbindung. ir hot nisht gevust

00:04:12.580 --> 00:04:13.839
NO, NO

00:04:14.200 --> 00:04:15.054
NO.

00:04:14.871 --> 00:04:16.404
tsi zi lebt tsi nisht.

00:04:15.904 --> 00:04:19.171
⟨zi hot⟩ nisht gevust fun mir, ⟨hob ikh⟩ nisht gevust fun ir. zi iz gevezn

00:04:19.464 --> 00:04:21.972
in NOVOSIBIRSK

00:04:22.165 --> 00:04:24.521
ALTAYSKIY KRAI heyst dos

00:04:24.578 --> 00:04:28.487
hot zi gearbet in a fabrik vu m'hot geneyt far militer di

00:04:29.421 --> 00:04:33.279
ober, ober ir ho- ir hot, ir hot dos d- oysgefunen nokh, nokh der krig.

00:04:32.053 --> 00:04:36.519
nakher. ikh hob nisht gevust UNK ikh bin geven farshikt in a koyl MINE, koyl shaft.

00:04:37.386 --> 00:04:40.181
dortn take dray yor bin ikh geven i-

00:04:40.423 --> 00:04:43.387
farshikt dortn bay di yapanishe grenets.

00:04:44.052 --> 00:04:46.664
az zogt mir nokh a mol, az in, in fertsik

00:04:46.664 --> 00:04:50.660
hot men aykh geshikt keyn GOMEL, un fun dortn avekgeshikt

00:04:50.363 --> 00:04:53.884
keyn k- in an andere tfise, keyn GORKI. fun GORKI

00:04:52.843 --> 00:04:53.917
GORKI

00:04:53.890 --> 00:04:59.520
keyn KOTLAS. dortn iz geven aza punkt vu m'hot ⟨tsunamen⟩genumen fun di tfises di mentshn

00:04:59.745 --> 00:05:01.933
un m'hot avekgeshikt in di lagern.

00:05:02.108 --> 00:05:03.823
ir veyst in Rusland

00:05:03.846 --> 00:05:05.392
iz gevezn

00:05:05.938 --> 00:05:08.838
m'hot gedorfn hobn arbeter, hot men arestirt mentshn

00:05:08.838 --> 00:05:11.088
iz in di lagern geven tsen milyon mentshn.

00:05:11.088 --> 00:05:12.041
arestirt.

00:05:12.300 --> 00:05:14.077
kh'veys nisht tsi me veyst dos.

00:05:14.077 --> 00:05:16.226
yede por kilometer geven a lager

00:05:16.300 --> 00:05:17.967
un s'iz geven a vertl

00:05:17.967 --> 00:05:19.330
vi m'hot gezogt

00:05:19.438 --> 00:05:24.376
TO NE BYL BUDET, A KTO BYL NIKOGDA NE ZABUDET. dos heyst

00:05:24.552 --> 00:05:28.016
az ver s'iz nisht geven nokh vet zayn in a lager.

00:05:28.016 --> 00:05:30.958
un ver s'iz geven in lager vet keyn mol nisht fargesn.

00:05:32.500 --> 00:05:35.008
ikh denk az ikh hob gut ibergezetst oyf

00:05:36.583 --> 00:05:40.779
iz gevezn, ikh bin, geven farshikte mentshn, milyonen mentshn.

00:05:41.224 --> 00:05:43.074
az vu zayt ir farshikt?

00:05:43.468 --> 00:05:45.048
vu ikh bin geven farshikt?

00:05:45.325 --> 00:05:49.133
ikh bin geven, zog ikh dokh, dos ershte bin ikh gevezn

00:05:49.375 --> 00:05:55.219
in, in di tfise. fun di tfise hot men geshikt, hot men gearbet in a lager, ARKHANGEL'SKIY OBLAST'

00:05:55.219 --> 00:05:58.788
hot men gemakht a, a ban LI- linye

00:05:58.788 --> 00:05:59.884
vu s'iz geforn

00:05:59.884 --> 00:06:02.120
hot men ⟨gedarft⟩ makhn a NASIL'

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:03.425
oysshitn erd

00:06:03.617 --> 00:06:06.631
hot men gekopet griber, un m'hot tsugefirt

00:06:06.705 --> 00:06:09.972
m'hot UNK vi nor heyst es? do vu es geyt a TRAIN, nu

00:06:10.958 --> 00:06:11.897
un

00:06:10.975 --> 00:06:13.028
az vi lang hot ir dos geton?

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:16.774
biz, biz nayn un fertsikstn yor

00:06:17.033 --> 00:06:19.253
vi, biz s'iz geven di amnestye

00:06:19.253 --> 00:06:22.713
ven di poylishe regirung in, fun England

00:06:22.838 --> 00:06:26.848
hot gemakht dem opmakh mit di sovyetn ven der daytsh iz ongefaln

00:06:27.377 --> 00:06:31.179
hot men, hot men geven an amnestye. m'hot di ale

00:06:31.179 --> 00:06:33.160
di poylishe birger bafrayt.

00:06:32.946 --> 00:06:35.690
az vu hot ir geboyt di, di banen?

00:06:35.882 --> 00:06:39.166
ARKHANGEL'SK, hot dos geheysn UNK

00:06:37.941 --> 00:06:39.200
vu iz dos?

00:06:39.426 --> 00:06:41.259
in Rusland, vu es iz.

00:06:40.354 --> 00:06:42.255
ober vu. s'iz Sibir?

00:06:41.552 --> 00:06:44.229
in Sibir, yo. dos UNK Sibir.

00:06:45.855 --> 00:06:48.532
un ir lay- zayt dortn geven etlekhe monatn?

00:06:46.378 --> 00:06:47.334
un ven

00:06:48.589 --> 00:06:53.561
dortn bin ikh gevezn efsher bay ts- bay elef, elef monatn

00:06:53.584 --> 00:06:54.860
in dem lager.

00:06:56.250 --> 00:06:58.893
biz, biz in oktober

00:06:58.950 --> 00:07:02.909
in oktober nayn un fertsikstn yor denk ikh iz geven di amnestye.

00:07:02.646 --> 00:07:06.285
vos iz geven di, vi zaynen geven di badingungen dortn in lager?

00:07:05.481 --> 00:07:06.420
shreklekh.

00:07:07.202 --> 00:07:09.052
shreklekh. ikh hob gegat

00:07:09.227 --> 00:07:10.351
a fal

00:07:11.067 --> 00:07:12.607
ven ikh hob gefirt

00:07:12.607 --> 00:07:14.683
a t- a tatshke mit erd

00:07:14.683 --> 00:07:18.536
ikh veys nisht vos ir veyst, a ⟨tatshke⟩, aza vegelekh mit tsvey hentlekh.

00:07:18.643 --> 00:07:22.248
ikh hob gedorfn tsufirn di erd. in vinter iz dos redl

00:07:22.575 --> 00:07:24.746
geven gefroyrn mit ayz

00:07:24.938 --> 00:07:27.598
un ikh hob zikh gegebn a glitsh. ikh bin gegan oyf a bret.

00:07:27.598 --> 00:07:30.368
ikh bin arayngefaln, un ikh hob gekrign a klap

00:07:30.912 --> 00:07:33.285
mit dem hentl, un ikh bin avek, ikh

00:07:33.308 --> 00:07:34.432
⟨farkhalesht⟩

00:07:34.573 --> 00:07:37.582
iz mayner a khaver aropgeshprungen. m'hot mikh

00:07:37.582 --> 00:07:38.905
oyfgemuntert

00:07:39.062 --> 00:07:42.569
un mikh aroysgenumen. m'hot mikh gefirt tsurik in lager

00:07:42.569 --> 00:07:44.270
dos iz geven bay UNK

00:07:44.293 --> 00:07:47.943
m'hot mir tsurikgefirt in lager, iz der dokter gevezn oykhet a f-

00:07:47.943 --> 00:07:49.243
a farmakhter

00:07:49.243 --> 00:07:51.393
a Varshever yid

00:07:51.393 --> 00:07:53.925
un dortn iz geven di gezets, der LAW

00:07:53.925 --> 00:07:56.965
az ir hot nisht keyn hits, ir hot nisht keyn fiber

00:07:56.965 --> 00:07:59.695
tor men aykh nisht bafrayen fun di arbet.

00:07:59.695 --> 00:08:01.945
iz er gekumen der, a, a

00:08:01.966 --> 00:08:05.286
a zelner hot mikh gebrengt, dos heyst a UNK

00:08:05.286 --> 00:08:06.346
oyf rusish

00:08:06.346 --> 00:08:10.511
hot mikh gebrengt in lager, gan tsum dokter, er zol mir zen vos me ken tun

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:14.865
hot der dokter gezen, zogt er "er hot nisht keyn hits, ken ikh im nisht bafrayen.

00:08:14.871 --> 00:08:17.413
der zelner iz shoyn aleyn gevorn beyz, zogt er

00:08:17.638 --> 00:08:19.708
"ON UNK UBYLSYA"

00:08:19.708 --> 00:08:23.028
s'heyst "er hot zikh shier derharget. vos heyst im geyn tsurik tsu di arbet?"

00:08:23.028 --> 00:08:25.969
der zelner hot ober gemuzt UNK gezogt "ikh tor nisht."

00:08:26.110 --> 00:08:29.580
der, er aleyn iz geven, hot gehat tsen yor UNK, der dokter

00:08:30.092 --> 00:08:32.287
hot men im, mir tsurikgefirt

00:08:32.287 --> 00:08:34.447
oyfn, oyf dem, tsu di arbet

00:08:34.447 --> 00:08:37.429
nor nisht, ikh hob nisht gearbet. m'hot gemakht a fayer dortn

00:08:37.429 --> 00:08:41.153
un ikh bin gezitsn shoyn biz ale zenen aheymgeganen, bin ikh oykh aheymganen.

00:08:41.153 --> 00:08:43.196
damolst bin ikh yetst krank gevorn

00:08:43.196 --> 00:08:46.202
un ikh bin gelign dray tog in shtarkn hits.

00:08:47.524 --> 00:08:49.408
s'iz geven dortn UNK

00:08:49.532 --> 00:08:53.053
un nokh a zakh iz geven in lager. zenen geven azolkhe

00:08:53.076 --> 00:08:54.724
untervelt mentshn

00:08:55.270 --> 00:08:57.879
un ven m'hot gedorfn grobn di griber

00:08:57.885 --> 00:08:59.904
hot men gekrign esn

00:08:59.927 --> 00:09:01.949
ACCORDING vifl m'hot gearbet

00:09:01.949 --> 00:09:03.599
vifl m'hot oysgearbet

00:09:04.146 --> 00:09:07.264
un i- ikh hob gearbet mit nokh eynem

00:09:07.264 --> 00:09:09.314
an estraykhishn

00:09:09.867 --> 00:09:12.462
men- mentsh vos er iz gevezn

00:09:12.462 --> 00:09:14.394
in Estraykh in SCHUTZBUND

00:09:14.394 --> 00:09:16.374
ikh veys nisht ir veyst a SCHUTZBUND.

00:09:16.374 --> 00:09:18.694
dos iz geven, es iz geven der oyfshtand

00:09:18.694 --> 00:09:21.197
in Estraykh in fir un draysikstn yor

00:09:21.197 --> 00:09:24.727
iz zenen a teyl fun di SCHUTZBUNDistn antlofn keyn Rusland

00:09:25.071 --> 00:09:28.392
heyst ⟨in⟩ dortn zikh tsu rateven, hot men im dort arestirt

00:09:28.392 --> 00:09:30.263
un er hot gekrign akht yor

00:09:30.471 --> 00:09:31.629
politish.

00:09:31.703 --> 00:09:36.135
iz er geven in lager, geven elter fun mir, ober zeyer en eydeler mentsh

00:09:36.445 --> 00:09:41.721
un ikh hob mit im gearbet. m'hot getun d- m'hot gearbet shver me zol kri- az m'hot gemakht di norme

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:46.951
hot men gekrign a shtikl fish oder dortn a b- a, nokh a b- a bisl besere zup

00:09:47.548 --> 00:09:51.389
iz gevezn eyner vos er hot gemostn dos, der onfirer

00:09:51.565 --> 00:09:55.642
iz gevezn dortn azolkhe khuliganes vos zey hobn gornisht getun

00:09:55.935 --> 00:09:57.385
un der, der

00:09:57.385 --> 00:10:01.205
der vos hot dos gemostn hot moyre gehat far zey, iz er dokh geven mit zey ⟨a⟩ khaver

00:10:01.205 --> 00:10:03.635
hot er fun undz tsugenumen. er hot zey tsugeleygt.

00:10:03.635 --> 00:10:05.975
zey hobn ge- az zey hobn gemakht a sakh

00:10:05.975 --> 00:10:09.356
iz zey hobn oysgekumen, UNK oysgekopet a grub, iz men geganen

00:10:09.356 --> 00:10:12.242
oysmestn bay farnakht, hot undz ge-

00:10:12.242 --> 00:10:15.488
un der estraykher hot zikh gut gekent, hot er ongehoybn

00:10:15.949 --> 00:10:20.415
tsu shrayen az s'iz nisht, az m'hot gemakht mer, hot men UNK nokh tseshlogn

00:10:20.573 --> 00:10:23.674
un m- un azoy iz gevezn di

00:10:23.674 --> 00:10:24.937
di situatsye.

00:10:27.036 --> 00:10:29.496
az ir zogt yetst iz geven an a- ame-

00:10:29.496 --> 00:10:31.687
amnestye in eyn un fertsik?

00:10:32.065 --> 00:10:32.720
vu?

00:10:32.588 --> 00:10:34.185
in, ye.

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:35.552
di amnestye iz geven in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:10:34.427 --> 00:10:37.205
az ir zent aroys fun, fun lager?

00:10:36.182 --> 00:10:39.466
ale, ale poylishe, poylishe birger

00:10:39.507 --> 00:10:43.635
ven di g- di regirung, in England, di poylishe regirung

00:10:43.725 --> 00:10:46.537
ven der daytsh iz ongefaln oyf di sovyetn

00:10:46.746 --> 00:10:51.178
⟨hobn⟩ di poylishe regirung geshlosn an opmakh mit di sovyetn

00:10:51.268 --> 00:10:54.873
un zey hobn gefodert me zol ale poylishe birger bafrayen.

00:10:55.420 --> 00:10:57.338
hot men undz bafrayt damolst.

00:10:57.293 --> 00:10:58.721
un vo

00:10:57.377 --> 00:10:58.940
nor shpeter

00:10:58.963 --> 00:11:02.129
hobn zey mikh getsvungen, ⟨un⟩ ikh bin gevezn

00:11:02.338 --> 00:11:06.264
in, bizn, d- bin ikh, ⟨vi⟩ m'hot undz bafrayt, bin ikh avek

00:11:06.456 --> 00:11:08.120
keyn KYRGYZIA

00:11:09.139 --> 00:11:11.310
un dortn hob ikh gearbet

00:11:11.653 --> 00:11:15.012
in s- d- i- yo, befor

00:11:15.012 --> 00:11:19.282
ven m'hot undz bafrayt, bin ikh geven in a shtot, hot zi geheysn AKTYUBINSK.

00:11:19.973 --> 00:11:24.017
in a gevisn tog zenen mir aroysgan in gas, iz geven aroysgeklept

00:11:24.411 --> 00:11:28.623
afishn az ale poylishe birger zoln zikh tsushteln

00:11:28.815 --> 00:11:31.728
tsu di poylishe armey vos hot zikh geshafn

00:11:32.173 --> 00:11:35.483
 d- er hot geheysn, d- der general

00:11:35.483 --> 00:11:37.553
ANDERS, ANDERS armey.

00:11:38.250 --> 00:11:41.558
nu, ⟨ikh bin⟩, als a poylishe birger, nu, ikh hob gevolt

00:11:41.558 --> 00:11:43.508
s- a mol tsurikkumen keyn Poyln

00:11:43.918 --> 00:11:46.288
bin ikh zikh tsugeshtelt in di armey

00:11:46.288 --> 00:11:48.678
un bin gevezn akht vokhn

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.304
un m- gevoynt hobn mir in di vagonen

00:11:51.934 --> 00:11:53.379
un

00:11:53.419 --> 00:11:55.169
m'hot undz avekgefirt

00:11:55.169 --> 00:11:58.089
biz UZBEKISTAN in a shtot vos zi heyst

00:11:58.089 --> 00:11:59.066
KAGAN.

00:11:59.730 --> 00:12:01.043
in KAGAN

00:12:01.043 --> 00:12:06.913
hot men gemakht dortn, undz aroysgerufn ale, yidn un polyakn, un s'iz gekumen a poylisher ofitsir

00:12:06.953 --> 00:12:08.398
un er hot gezogt

00:12:09.703 --> 00:12:11.637
"WYZNANIE MOJZESZOWE

00:12:12.032 --> 00:12:14.132
⟨PI⟩ PROWOSLAWNE"

00:12:14.132 --> 00:12:18.482
dos heyst yidn un PROWOS- un, un PROWOSLAWn zoln aroysgeyn

00:12:18.799 --> 00:12:22.809
az yidn un PROWOSLAWn vet men yetst nisht nemen, nor bloyz polyakn.

00:12:23.389 --> 00:12:28.220
un m'hot undz, m'hot ongehoybn protestirn, ober s'hot gornisht geholfn. m'hot undz bazaytikt.

00:12:28.220 --> 00:12:29.157
di yidn

00:12:29.157 --> 00:12:33.002
un PROWOSLO- vaysrusn, ukrayner, azolkhe PROWOSLAWn.

00:12:34.189 --> 00:12:36.697
m'iz, ho- ⟨zenen mir⟩ avekgeforn

00:12:37.395 --> 00:12:42.319
in a sh- m'hot undz avekgefirt eygntlekh. dortn fort men nisht aleyn. me firt UNK

00:12:42.319 --> 00:12:44.780
m'hot undz avekgefirt biz KYRGYZIA.

00:12:45.377 --> 00:12:49.185
in KY- KYRGYZIA hob ikh gearbet in a KOLKHOZ

00:12:49.782 --> 00:12:51.919
bizn dray un fertsikstn yor.

00:12:51.807 --> 00:12:54.737
vi lang hot dos genumen tsu forn biz keyn KYRGYZIA?

00:12:54.979 --> 00:12:56.272
a por tog.

00:12:57.173 --> 00:12:58.466
iz

00:12:58.827 --> 00:13:01.757
un oyfn KOLKHOZ hot ir gearbet ⟨oyf a⟩ tsvey yor?

00:13:01.476 --> 00:13:05.334
NO, UNK KOLKHOZ hob ikh gearbet fun eyn un fertsik

00:13:05.745 --> 00:13:07.325
biz dray un fertsik.

00:13:07.551 --> 00:13:14.126
in dray un fertsikstn yor hobn zey undz getsvungen di poylishe birger aroystsunemen sovetishe peser.

00:13:14.048 --> 00:13:16.997
ven ir zaynt geven in, oyfn KOLKHOZ

00:13:16.997 --> 00:13:20.319
zent ir geven fray oder nokh a gefangener?

00:13:19.127 --> 00:13:20.339
i- d- fray.

00:13:20.339 --> 00:13:22.834
fray. nokh di amnestye bin ikh geven fray.

00:13:23.076 --> 00:13:26.749
az ven ir volt gevolt avekgeyn ergets andersh, volt ir gekent?

00:13:26.164 --> 00:13:29.583
dos iz geven shver. dos hot ir gedorfn hobn a derloybenish.

00:13:30.214 --> 00:13:34.882
UNK ⟨az ir zent⟩ geven fray un az ir hot gevolt avekgeyn fun di arbet, hot ir gemuzt hobn a derloybenish.

00:13:35.850 --> 00:13:40.366
az bay di arbet zent ir d- s'iz dortn geven vekhter, UNK geven fartsoymt?

00:13:39.478 --> 00:13:41.551
NO, NO, NO, NO.

00:13:40.542 --> 00:13:41.633
nisht azoy.

00:13:41.551 --> 00:13:42.985
s'iz nisht geven. s'iz geven

00:13:42.985 --> 00:13:46.459
in KYRGYZIA zenen mir geven a por hundert BEZHENITSes

00:13:46.482 --> 00:13:47.356
yidn

00:13:47.356 --> 00:13:49.141
fun UNK, fun Poyln.

00:13:49.401 --> 00:13:52.871
un ir zaynt geven tsuzamen nokh mit, mit di kuzinen fun der vayb?

00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:54.238
un

00:13:53.620 --> 00:13:54.390
NO

00:13:54.497 --> 00:13:55.118
o-

00:13:55.088 --> 00:13:58.728
ikh UNK alts, keynem nisht. ikh bin geblibn al- aleyn.

00:13:55.118 --> 00:13:56.735
UNK fraynt?

00:13:58.728 --> 00:14:00.488
⟨fun⟩ dos alts iz gevorn tseshikt.

00:14:01.028 --> 00:14:02.625
farshidene lagern.

00:14:03.559 --> 00:14:06.405
un fun di, mayne kuzinen vos zenen mit mir avek

00:14:06.748 --> 00:14:09.070
iz eyner arayn in di

00:14:09.381 --> 00:14:10.725
in di armey

00:14:11.085 --> 00:14:13.880
in WANDA WASILEWSKA's armey.

00:14:14.933 --> 00:14:19.112
dos iz geven shpeter hot ge- in Rusland geshafn a poylishe armey

00:14:19.607 --> 00:14:23.364
iz, un er iz umgekumen, ge- in, oyfn front.

00:14:24.450 --> 00:14:27.886
az ir hot gearbet oyfn KOLKHOZ k- kimat a ts-

00:14:25.986 --> 00:14:30.671
un der tsveyter bruder lebt yetst in, der RAYTER lebt yetst in Yisroel.

00:14:29.361 --> 00:14:30.519
mh

00:14:30.677 --> 00:14:35.396
un az ir ven gezen, geven oyfn KOLKHOZ, vu hot ir gevoynt, un vos hot ir gegesn?

00:14:34.812 --> 00:14:41.370
ikh hob ge- in KOLKHOZ iz grade dort hobn mir gehat nisht laykht. mir hobn gearbet, ikh hob gearbet dort fun KOLKHOZ

00:14:41.376 --> 00:14:43.226
in a UNK

00:14:43.435 --> 00:14:49.886
dos heyst in a plats vu, vu KOLKHOZNIKes brengen di tvue vos zey nemen arop fun di felder

00:14:49.886 --> 00:14:51.883
firt men zey oyf dem plats

00:14:52.024 --> 00:14:55.463
un dortn vert dos sortirt, un es vert avekgeshikt

00:14:55.463 --> 00:14:57.671
tsum front dortn farshidene

00:14:57.880 --> 00:15:01.620
un ikh hob gegat ge- dortn gut tsu esn. ikh hob dort gehat nisht shlekht.

00:15:01.845 --> 00:15:06.176
gevoynt hobn mir bay a rusishn FAMILY, ikh mit m- nokh a khaver

00:15:06.013 --> 00:15:07.374
vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:15:07.380 --> 00:15:09.635
di F- di, di F- di F-

00:15:08.781 --> 00:15:11.593
di mishpokhe d- vos, mit velkhe ir hot gevoynt.

00:15:11.650 --> 00:15:15.204
vi iz, der a- der khaver vos hot mir ge- ⟨mit⟩ mir geven

00:15:14.333 --> 00:15:17.803
vi ho- NO, di, dortn vu ir hot gevoynt. vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:15:16.206 --> 00:15:19.980
oh, zey hobn geheysn NADYA, NADYA

00:15:20.239 --> 00:15:21.600
⟨LIMANOSOVA⟩

00:15:22.180 --> 00:15:23.771
NADYA ⟨LIMANOSOVA⟩

00:15:23.771 --> 00:15:26.847
der man, zi iz ge- sh- der man iz geven oyfn front

00:15:27.377 --> 00:15:32.653
er iz umgekumen in, bar a shtot KERCH, iz geven a shtarker klap

00:15:32.963 --> 00:15:37.108
mit di daytshn. dort iz er umgekumen. s'iz gekumen az- a meldung

00:15:37.536 --> 00:15:42.339
fun di armey az der man iz umgekumen. di froy iz gevezn a NURSE

00:15:42.649 --> 00:15:44.837
un s'iz geven zayns a muter.

00:15:44.978 --> 00:15:46.761
zeyer a voyle froy

00:15:47.020 --> 00:15:51.401
an eltere froy. zi hot undz gehaltn, mikh mit mayn khaver, azoy vi kinder

00:15:51.998 --> 00:15:55.316
UNK m'hot dortn gevoynt biz, biz m'hot mikh

00:15:55.626 --> 00:15:59.265
⟨m'hot mir⟩ getsvungen undz aroystsunemen rusishe peser

00:15:59.828 --> 00:16:03.076
azoy hobn zey undz di rusn nisht gekent mobilizirn

00:16:03.076 --> 00:16:05.446
vayl mir zenen geven poylishe birger

00:16:05.446 --> 00:16:09.350
hot men getsvungen undz tsu nemen rusishe d- peser

00:16:09.350 --> 00:16:11.324
un m'hot mir gegebn a pas.

00:16:11.324 --> 00:16:13.341
kh'hob nisht gevolt, hot ⟨men⟩ mikh ayngezetst

00:16:13.341 --> 00:16:14.739
oyf finef yor

00:16:15.353 --> 00:16:19.177
un m'hot mikh mobilizirt avek in di koyl MINES

00:16:19.504 --> 00:16:24.493
keyn, dos vu ikh ho- zog aykh dortn bay di yapanishe grenets. dortn zenen mir geforn efsher tsvey vokhn.

00:16:25.613 --> 00:16:27.463
vi hot es geheysn dos ort?

00:16:27.250 --> 00:16:30.416
dos ort hot geheysn CHITINSKAYA OBLAST'

00:16:30.861 --> 00:16:32.897
CHERNISHEVSKIY RAYON

00:16:33.190 --> 00:16:35.541
STANTSYA K- BUKACHACHA

00:16:35.541 --> 00:16:38.308
SHACHTA NOMER DVA. ikh gedenk dem adres.

00:16:40.665 --> 00:16:42.464
dort bin ikh geven dray yor.

00:16:43.703 --> 00:16:44.676
un d-

00:16:43.737 --> 00:16:45.168
ir gedenkt

00:16:45.168 --> 00:16:47.519
dem man mit velkhn ir hot

00:16:47.519 --> 00:16:51.109
ir zent geblibn bay der mishpokhe in, in, in KOLKHOZ

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:50.734
yo, ⟨dem⟩ BLAKHER.

00:16:51.109 --> 00:16:52.624
vi hot er geheysn?

00:16:51.651 --> 00:16:53.619
BLAKHER, Dovid BLAKHER.

00:16:53.035 --> 00:16:53.906
BLAKHER.

00:16:54.047 --> 00:16:57.604
er UNK lebn. ikh hob im nokh di milkhome getrofn.

00:16:54.587 --> 00:16:55.256
ye

00:16:57.604 --> 00:16:58.867
in Daytshland

00:16:59.008 --> 00:17:03.912
in STUTTGART. hot geheyrat mit a rusish yidishe froy.

00:17:00.257 --> 00:17:01.280
ir zent

00:17:04.594 --> 00:17:08.773
ir zent farshikt tsuzamen mit im keyn Yapan? UNK

00:17:07.497 --> 00:17:12.334
NO. er iz geven f- er iz fun an andere shtot, un ikh hob zikh mit im bafrayndet in di tfise

00:17:12.728 --> 00:17:15.692
un nokh di tfise zenen mir tsuzamen geven in lager

00:17:15.951 --> 00:17:21.101
un fun lager vu m'hot undz bafrayt, zenen mir geven tsunezamen, geshlofn in eyn bet

00:17:21.101 --> 00:17:22.711
un gegesn un gegat

00:17:22.711 --> 00:17:24.804
alts tsunezamen azoy vi brider.

00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:30.980
un nakher, mikh hot men mobilizirt dortn, un im hot men mobilizirt in an andere gegnt.

00:17:31.780 --> 00:17:35.368
ober nokh di milkhome hob ikh im getrofn in, in Daytshland.

00:17:34.902 --> 00:17:38.305
az ir hot gevoy- i- or hot gearbet in di shakhtn dray yor?

00:17:37.872 --> 00:17:38.625
ye.

00:17:38.952 --> 00:17:40.228
vos hot ir geton?

00:17:40.487 --> 00:17:41.158
ikh b-

00:17:41.158 --> 00:17:48.041
in shakhtn iz gevezn nisht keyn moderne. s'iz geven ⟨d- dort a⟩ tekhnik azoy tsurikgeshtanen.

00:17:48.587 --> 00:17:53.120
m'hot gedorfn aropgeyn in di shakhtn a halbn kilometer tsu fus

00:17:53.498 --> 00:17:54.336
tif

00:17:55.405 --> 00:18:00.039
un in di shakhtn iz gevezn biz dan, biz tsu di kni vaser

00:18:00.788 --> 00:18:04.303
un dortn in di gegnt hot gornisht gevaksn

00:18:04.303 --> 00:18:08.240
s'iz geven tsvey monatn in zumer, hot men gevaksn bloyz

00:18:08.263 --> 00:18:11.193
burikes, vayse, vayse burikes.

00:18:11.284 --> 00:18:16.391
ale di esnvarg hot men gedorfn tsubrengen fun CHITA, fun rayon.

00:18:16.853 --> 00:18:19.749
m'hot gez- dos iz geven dray un fertsikstn yor

00:18:20.650 --> 00:18:22.652
hobn mentshn undz dertseylt

00:18:22.843 --> 00:18:26.097
az in tsvey un fertsikstn yor, dortn iz geven a lager

00:18:26.097 --> 00:18:27.798
fun undzer, farmakhte

00:18:28.142 --> 00:18:32.405
az in di shakhtn az m'hot geharget mentshn, m'hot gegesn mentshn fleysh.

00:18:33.137 --> 00:18:35.476
nor ven mir zenen ahingekumen

00:18:35.584 --> 00:18:38.278
iz oykhet di lage geven zeyer a shvere.

00:18:39.077 --> 00:18:40.016
nor

00:18:40.242 --> 00:18:42.801
m'hot zikh bamit. m'hot ahingebrengt

00:18:43.515 --> 00:18:46.545
shpeter hot men ahingebrengt yapanezer

00:18:46.545 --> 00:18:50.325
UNK f- do, fun di milkhome, ven Rusland iz ongefaln oyf ⟨Yaponye⟩

00:18:50.485 --> 00:18:52.498
hot men gebrengt dortn ahin

00:18:52.498 --> 00:18:59.038
hobn zey mitgebrengt farshidene zakhn. m'hot dortn g- prubirt oystoyshn di derfer mit mentshn, azoy az m'hot nisht ge-

00:18:59.038 --> 00:19:01.338
zh- ⟨der⟩ shpeter iz gevezn shlekht.

00:19:01.521 --> 00:19:04.147
un Amerike hot geshlosn an opmakh

00:19:04.305 --> 00:19:07.032
mit Rusland ven der daytsh iz ongefaln

00:19:07.208 --> 00:19:08.856
hot men shoyn gebrengt

00:19:09.452 --> 00:19:11.673
produktn, Amerikaner

00:19:11.848 --> 00:19:17.413
durkh, durkh a, durkh di, vi hot dos geheysn? IR- nisht durkh IRKUTSK

00:19:17.413 --> 00:19:19.672
dortn do a groyse, groyse s-

00:19:20.286 --> 00:19:21.649
oh, fargesn.

00:19:21.649 --> 00:19:24.037
hot men gebrengt Amerikaner produktn

00:19:24.037 --> 00:19:25.984
hot men gebrengt vays mel.

00:19:26.293 --> 00:19:29.966
a broyt fun a kilo, a SHAKTYOR hot gekrign a kilo broyt

00:19:30.107 --> 00:19:31.636
iz geven azoy groys

00:19:32.318 --> 00:19:36.024
un demolst i- hot men shoyn nisht gehungert. dos iz geven

00:19:36.553 --> 00:19:38.622
bizn zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:19:39.692 --> 00:19:41.643
az genoy vos hot ir geton?

00:19:41.650 --> 00:19:42.707
als a

00:19:41.683 --> 00:19:45.642
ikh hob gearbet in shakht, hob ikh gearbet akht monatn. kh'hob gesh-

00:19:45.717 --> 00:19:48.363
ikh vil dort shildern vi a shakht zet oys.

00:19:48.363 --> 00:19:49.417
a shakht hot

00:19:49.417 --> 00:19:51.026
azolekhe sloyen

00:19:51.049 --> 00:19:52.730
in di, in di erd

00:19:52.855 --> 00:19:56.201
iz do a, teyl mol iz do a g- aza min sloy vos er hot

00:19:56.201 --> 00:19:57.556
a halbn meter

00:19:57.681 --> 00:20:01.961
a meter, oder teyl mol f- iz do a groyser sloy iz do mer koyln.

00:20:02.288 --> 00:20:06.416
iz UNK iz gekumen aropshikn arop mentshn vos zey heysn

00:20:06.540 --> 00:20:09.318
⟨BORISHCHIKES⟩. zey boyen oys lekher

00:20:09.460 --> 00:20:10.989
in di koyln

00:20:11.113 --> 00:20:13.621
un dortn leygt men arayn dinamit

00:20:13.898 --> 00:20:17.908
me shikt arop ZAPALSHCHIKE heyst dos, di vos zey raysn oyf

00:20:18.083 --> 00:20:20.450
un leygn arayn dortn DYNAMITE

00:20:20.450 --> 00:20:25.231
un nakher bindt men tsunezamen di lektrishe drotn. me farklept

00:20:25.542 --> 00:20:27.532
un s'iz do aza RUBIL'NIK

00:20:27.532 --> 00:20:30.942
elektrishe. me geyt avek hundert meter, tor men nisht shteyn.

00:20:30.942 --> 00:20:32.639
ven er git dos a loz arop

00:20:33.186 --> 00:20:34.682
rayst dos oyf

00:20:33.287 --> 00:20:34.310
UNK

00:20:34.890 --> 00:20:36.971
hobn undz gedorfn arayngeyn

00:20:36.971 --> 00:20:41.769
un nemen di koyln aroysshitn. zenen farforn vegelekh, azolkhe vagones

00:20:41.978 --> 00:20:46.748
un aroyfshitn di koyln oyf di vegelekh, un dos i- di vegelekh zenen tsugeganen oyf

00:20:46.748 --> 00:20:49.328
ferd. ale ferd zenen geven blind dort.

00:20:49.639 --> 00:20:52.636
zenen geganen tsu tsu aza gevisn plats

00:20:52.879 --> 00:20:56.113
vu di vegelekh, hintn iz geshtanen a groyser WAGON

00:20:56.372 --> 00:20:59.336
hot men zikh ibergedreyt. s'hot geheysn a ⟨PERESKIP⟩

00:20:59.713 --> 00:21:02.368
un, un s'iz geganen tsvey azolkhe

00:21:02.368 --> 00:21:06.322
shtrik vos ⟨eyner⟩ WAGON iz geganen arop un eyner aroyf ⟨fun⟩ di heykh

00:21:06.885 --> 00:21:10.257
iz geganen tsvey groyse vagonen, un dortn untn

00:21:10.257 --> 00:21:16.062
iz geshtanen aza groyser WAGON. di vegelekh, az m'hot tsugefirt a vegele iz geven a UNK a kleyns

00:21:16.062 --> 00:21:17.645
un s'hot zikh oysgeshit

00:21:17.719 --> 00:21:20.632
un di zenen ganen a ⟨gantser⟩ tog arop un aroyf.

00:21:20.672 --> 00:21:22.902
un s'iz keyn mentshn nisht geven

00:21:22.902 --> 00:21:25.682
hot men gemuzt arbetn tsvey ZMYANes.

00:21:25.682 --> 00:21:28.107
befor hobn mir gearbet dray, akht sho

00:21:28.107 --> 00:21:31.347
m- ven ts- mir zenen ahingekumen iz nisht geven keyn mentshn.

00:21:31.347 --> 00:21:34.565
es hobn gearbet meydlekh fun zekhtsn yor oykhet in ⟨shakht⟩

00:21:34.565 --> 00:21:35.837
mobilizirte.

00:21:36.214 --> 00:21:39.161
⟨hot men⟩ gemuzt arbetn tsvelef sho

00:21:39.218 --> 00:21:42.108
fun akht in di fri biz akht oyf di nakht.

00:21:42.108 --> 00:21:47.041
ven undz ze'mir aroys iz arayn a tsveyte ZMYANA fun akhte bay nakht biz akhte in di fri.

00:21:46.710 --> 00:21:49.927
hot ir moyre gehat aruntertsukrikhn in erd?

00:21:48.988 --> 00:21:53.955
